<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/emma-regan> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Emma is an accomplished commercial leader who began her career at Nuclear Restoration Services (NRS) in the late 1990s. After working extensively across the NDA group and with government stakeholders, Emma rejoined NRS in 2019 to lead the Future Missions team. In 2023 Emma became the Commercial Director for NRS, joining the NRS Executive team. Emma champions diversity and inclusivity and serves as the Executive Sponsor for the NRS Women’s Network."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
